data.description: Welcome to this charming 1-story home nestled in a tranquil cul-de-sac, offering both comfort and convenience. Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths, this residence features a thoughtfully designed open floor plan, providing a seamless flow throughout the living spaces. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is adorned with elegant granite countertops and equipped with modern stainless steel appliances, enhancing both style and functionality. Enjoy the serenity of a quiet school district, providing an ideal environment for families. Beyond the confines of this peaceful abode, residents have easy access to local amenities, ensuring a lifestyle of convenience. The fully fenced backyard creates a private oasis for relaxation. This home harmoniously combines modern living with a touch of tranquility, offering a haven for those seeking the perfect blend of comfort and accessibility.
